.TH SHOAL-SECRET 1 "July 2026" "Shoal 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
shoal-secret \- manage encrypted Shoal secrets
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B shoal-secret set
.I name
.br
.B shoal-secret list
.br
.B shoal-secret delete
.I name
.SH DESCRIPTION
Stores an exact secret value read from standard input, lists names, or deletes a named value.
Secret values are never printed by this command.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR shoal (1)
